AHK SCRIPT:

Custom HotKeys:
^+q::  =  control + shift + q
       = closes hl2.exe, makes msg box, relaunches desktop, ends AHK script

^!+r:: =  control + alt + shift + r
       =  runs cmd.exe
              NOTES:  
                 regedit = registry editor
                 gpedit.msc = local group policy editor
